<li id="cite_note-3"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Udone-shima was inhabited during the <a href="/wiki/Meiji_era" title="Meiji era">Meiji era</a>.</span>
