</li>
<li id="cite_note-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.volcano.si.edu/world/region.cfm?rnum=0804">Volcanoes of the Izu, Volcano and Mariana Islands</a></span>
