<li id="cite_note-Kuriyama-etal-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Kuriyama-etal_7-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Kuriyama-etal_7-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1067248974"/><cite id="CITEREFKuriyamaBrandleyKatayamaMori2011" class="citation journal cs1">Kuriyama, Takeo; Brandley, Matthew C.; Katayama, Akira; Mori, Akira; Honda, Masanao; Hasegawa, Masami (2011). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://mattbrandley.com/pubs/Kuriyama_et_al_2011_JBio.pdf">"A time-calibrated phylogenetic approach to assessing the phylogeography, colonization history and phenotypic evolution of snakes in the Japanese Izu Islands"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i>J. Biogeogr</i>. <b>38</b> (2): 259–271. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1111%2Fj.1365-2699.2010.02403.x">10.1111/j.1365-2699.2010.02403.x</a>. <a href="/wiki/S2CID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="S2CID (identifier)">S2CID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://api.semanticscholar.org/CorpusID:55266255">55266255</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=J.+Biogeogr.&amp;rft.atitle=A+time-calibrated+phylogenetic+approach+to+assessing+the+phylogeography%2C+colonization+history+and+phenotypic+evolution+of+snakes+in+the+Japanese+Izu+Islands&amp;rft.volume=38&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=259-271&amp;rft.date=2011&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1111%2Fj.1365-2699.2010.02403.x&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.semanticscholar.org%2FCorpusID%3A55266255%23id-name%3DS2CID&amp;rft.aulast=Kuriyama&amp;rft.aufirst=Takeo&amp;rft.au=Brandley%2C+Matthew+C.&amp;rft.au=Katayama%2C+Akira&amp;rft.au=Mori%2C+Akira&amp;rft.au=Honda%2C+Masanao&a